00:19:51.566 --> 00:19:51.736 A:middle
neatly.

00:19:52.516 --> 00:19:56.736 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:19:57.236 --> 00:19:58.766 A:middle
But what about the image?

00:19:59.516 --> 00:20:01.346 A:middle
See the image has no text in it

00:19:59.516 --> 00:20:01.346 A:middle
See the image has no text in it

